Among the drivers, however, "sportswashing" - using sport to divert attention away from human rights issues - was not on the agendaThe Dakar gets under way with Saturday's prologue ahead of 12 stages, with a rest day on January 9The 43rd Dakar sees a new class joining the collection of cars, bikes, quads, trucks, buggies and SSVs - with the Dakar Classic category limited to vehicles from the 1980s and 90s